### 로그인 요청 (Login)
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test",
  "password": "111111"
}

### 토큰 갱신 요청 (Refresh Token)
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ0ZXN0IiwiZXhwIjoxNzQwOTg2NTUwLCJzY29wZSI6InJlZnJlc2gifQ.w5GJtmucGCrWjKxzFTOXexPU9y0O9fFt_VOUvkizks8"
}

### 로그아웃 요청 (Logout)
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test",
  "refresh_token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ0ZXN0IiwiZXhwIjoxNzQwOTg2NTUwLCJzY29wZSI6InJlZnJlc2gifQ.w5GJtmucGCrWjKxzFTOXexPU9y0O9fFt_VOUvkizks8"
}
